  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view captures a vibrant sunset over a cityscape and bay. The sky is dramatically colored with fiery reds and oranges blending into deep purples and blues higher up. Wispy clouds streak across the horizon, catching the last rays of sunlight and creating a textured, layered effect. Below the sky, a city sprawls along the bay, illuminated with twinkling lights. Silhouetted trees and foliage occupy the foreground, adding depth and framing the scene. The water of the bay reflects the colors of the sky, creating a sense of expansive beauty.",
